<h3>🚀 Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li>🎛️ A composable <code>Controller</code> base and focused traits — params, pagination, languages, routing, status, Twig, JSON/CBOR.</li>
    <li>🧩 Typed request-parameter extraction &amp; strategies — <code>ParamsTrait</code>, <code>ParamsStrategyTrait</code>, the <code>getParam*()</code> helpers.</li>
    <li>📥 File responses — download, streaming, HTTP range, ETag &amp; 304 Not Modified, content headers.</li>
    <li>🗜️ Archives, uploads &amp; encryption — zip/tar, file upload and OpenSSL file encryption.</li>
    <li>🛡️ CSRF, HTTP cache and language negotiation on top of Slim &amp; Twig.</li>
    <li>🧪 100% unit-test line coverage.</li>
</ul>

<h3>📦 Installation</h3>
<p>This library requires <a href="https://php.net/releases/" target="_blank">PHP 8.4+</a> and is installed via <a href="https://getcomposer.org/" target="_blank">Composer</a>:</p>
<pre class="language-bash prettyprint">composer require oihana/php-controllers</pre>

